i cant talk to some of you anymore. please dont take it personaly. its for my benefit. there have been good times, and i wont forget them. unfortunately. as for you- i love you. and i am going to do everything i can not to hate you. and to not hate your memories. and to not hate myself. i dont want to talk bad of you. i dont want to talk sourly of us. i honestly, dont want to say goodbye. but youve made that choice for me. please respect me. my memory. everything i gave you. do not let me be just another girl. please never call me number seven. please thank your mother. i love her. she has done a lot for me. and i never got to repay or thank her. she filled a void. its going to really hurt to lose her. who am i kidding? its going to really hurt to live with out knowing if youre alive or not. but i dont think i want to know if youre alive or not. i will never be the same again. i promise that. and my promises are real. i feel dirty. i am disgusted with myself. how dare i let this happen. how dare you let it happen. the lies were unnessary. further withdrawl of them will be apprecated. hey, stranger who i will never breathe a word of again. who will cloud all my thoughts. who will appear in my dreams, and in my tears. who will become a man with no name, with no face, with no life. i love you. and it digusts me to know i always will. it turns my stomach to know that you were the one. and that you left. i never say goodbye. for i warrent long goodbyes. i mean goodbyes. and they hurt. goodbye.

now, dont get me wrong i completely expected to cry [ because if you know anything about me at all or have known me for any substantial amount of time you know that i have never had a normal birthday ] so picture it march 17th 2004 [night before birthday] eleven forty five pm - i was at taco bell and realized what time it was and freaked out cos i figured that jeff had already shown up at my place and left pissed off cos i was there eleven fifty pm - RUSH home and try calling jeff like six times, cant get through (first cry fit here) midnight - vanessa calls, jeff calls *happy birthday jessica* one am - jeffrey gets here two am - sleep eight am - i'm awake and writing a paper one pm - i go to class two pm - i return from class three pm - jeffrey finally wakes up and gets out of bed three thirty pm- we go to big boy four thirty pm - we get back from big boy five pm - jeffrey leaves now lets sum up at this point : ive seen jeff for four hours total awake and he leaves to go home because he has band practice - which i totally understand only because he has shows this weekend - BUT after being ignored for the band for ten days straight (due to more show situations) i got a wee bit touchy over fact that the band comes before me even on my birthday- (insert crying fit number two here) six pm - jakboiee comes to get me six thirty pm - we go bowling eight pm - we go to hunan house nine thirty pm - we go to the movies [welcome to mooseport bleh movie] (quickly insert tears in dark theatre here) eleven thirty pm - come home and try to sleep one am - actually end up going to bed two am - amber comes home with a plethora of drunk people who i cant see two ten am- ambers drunk boyfriend attacks me in my bed two ten am and fifteen seconds - amber screams and beats boyfriend (crying on the phone with jeff cos the situation is weird and uncomfortable) three am - amber and gang leave for food [lil' chef] three thirty am - i fall asleep four fifteen am - i get a series of calls from amber that i try to ignore.. then she starts leaving messages on the dorm answering machine crying and begging for help quick filler story: john, ambers boyfriend, by some magical feat ended up at cmu with all his friends they were all incredibly drunk.. there was apparently some fight between some boys over amber at random party and it continued while they ate at lil' chef and so john took his friends car keys and left, only he didnt take the car... he just started walking. john was gone for over an hour by the time amber called me. four thirty am - i go and get my car to get amber and johns friends cos they are abandoned at the restaurant.. i see john walking while im going to my car/cant get his attention and he starts walking incredibly quickly away from me four forty am - amber, myself and one of johns friends [danny] drive around the entire city of mount pleasant looking for john five am - i get pulled over. the cops had been following me for a good ten minutes and finally wanted to know what was up and pulled me over cop story: the officer pulls me over and tells me i made an illegal left turn. i ask how thats possible and he says, what he MEANT was that i wasnt completely in the left turn lane and he admitted that i wouldnt know because there was snow on the ground and everyone knows you have no clue where the lines are on freshly snowed on streets. he says hes been following me and wanted to know why id been driving in circles - i explain to him that we are looking for a drunk boy who is possibly dangerous due to his drunkenness and anger. cop pulls up my record and comes back to talk he asks me if ive been drinking and i almost start laughing and reply "no sir i havent drank in well over four years" he says thats good to hear from a college student and then progresses on that he can smell liquor in my car.. amber and danny are forced into admitting that they are both trashed. cop thanks me for being the driver gives me my shit back and says if he sees john he will personally drop him off at my dorms front desk. five thirty am- danny amber and i come back to the dorm five thirty one am- i find john passed out coma like in a ball in front of our door and go and get amber and danny from down stairs five thirty five am- danny beats the fuck out of john in the hall way five forty til six am - lots of screaming beating fighting crying calling going on in the other room seven am - i finally fall asleep seven thirty am- i get up to go to my eight am class, collapse on the floor and decide its better to just go to bed (cry) eleven am- finally get up, puke some water up take some midol and shower. get the worst cramps ever and crumple over in pain (cry) two pm- go to class to take an exam, which i failed miserably three pm- return to dorm john tries to talk to me and apologize and such i get pissy and tell him its better off not to talk to me at all - he wishes me a happy birthday, belated, and hides in ambers room currently - amber comes home from class grabs john by his hair drags him to the door and screams that they need to talk, they are out in the hall screaming and crying now hi? ive been coughing up blood and sneezing blood all day. end of story. well .. at least my birthday is over.
